code: @Override protected RestChannelConsumer prepareRequest(RestRequest restRequest, NodeClient client) throws IOException {     SearchRequest searchRequest = new SearchRequest().     restRequest.withContentOrSourceParamParserOrNull(parser -> RestSearchAction.parseSearchRequest(searchRequest, restRequest, parser, size -> searchRequest.source().size(size))).
